headline: 4 Key Agriculture Stocks Positioned for Gains as Market Trends Improve
summary: The Agriculture - Operations industry is set to grow on innovation and rising demand for healthy products despite challenges from increasing costs and trade uncertainties. Companies such as CTVA, DOLE, AGRO and CVGW are well-positioned to benefit from these trends.
